    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A chitosan derivative with an amphoteric character that has the potential to improve paper strength and form films with a good barrier to gases and antibacterial activity. In conservation, it is used as a paper consolidant.</Note_Text>
